	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64185575">These are the kinds of questions and inquiries that one expects of journalism.  (Wired, for all their flash and hyperbole about THE NEXT BIG THING!!! does engage in serious journalism via its long-form reporting.)  As AI proliferates, expect journalism to decline even further, to the point where no one would even bother asking these kinds of questions to hold powerful people to account.  (Or: people will ask, but won't have the means or freedom to spent weeks or months investigating.  It amounts to the same thing.)</div>
	</div>

